title: Sambal Teriyaki Prawn & Chicken Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice, Sugar Snaps and Sesame Seeds
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sambal Teriyaki Chicken Stir-Fry in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
